'''Countdown Perch''' is a {{Rarity|Limited}} fish found in special pools in the [[Ocean]] during the [[Golden Tide]] event.

== Description ==
{{Description|This peculiar perch species appears as the Golden Tide approaches, with markings on its fins that seem to shift and change like the hands of a clock. Legend says it can sense the turning of the tide.|Bestiary Entry}}

